We are family of 5 and stayed for 2 days in 2 bedroom with pool villa. We felt excited from the ride on buggy after check-in, and the excited feeling lasted until we had left. We could have breakfast in the villa, but the view from the restaurant, "the terraced rice field', was good enough to go out to restaurant for breakfast. Also, the complementary afternoon tea provided in the same place was good enough. It was very useful that the shuttle was always available at any time up to Ubud city. However, the traffic in Ubud city was so crowded that it look somewhat more time to get to the city than we had expected. During the stay, I loved the free minibar and dialy refilled fruit basket. However, the pool of villa was 1.8m deep, which made it difficult for young childern to use it, but all the other facillities including spa bath and the amenity, and the kindness of staff was one of the best experiences I've ever had. I hope I can visit again.

5,0/526 Jul 2017
Verified traveler
My husband and I had such a heavenly time at this resort. The staff was so friendly and helpful, they always knew our names and were extremely helpful and polite. They were very attentive and knew anytime we left our room so they could do turn down service early and quickly. The grounds are tropical and lush. The villas are very private, lots of space, and quite frankly, nicer than the over-water bungalows that we stayed in for our honeymoon. This is one of the nicest villas we've been lucky to stay in. For what you pay, you get so much! The villa is gorgeous and so spacious. Your own personal plunge pool with a patio, a covered pagoda to relax in the shade overlooks a pond with coi. The room itself is also very spacious with an equally impressive bathroom. Fresh fruit is in your room every day and you can let them know what you like/don't like. Free breakfast is included and you can opt to have breakfast served in your villa. Free shuttle service to town anytime. They offer free activities like yoga, hiking, etc. We did the yoga; very relaxing way to start the day. We often didn't see guests and felt so relaxed the entire time. The restaurant at the resort is one of the most famous in Ubud, which was a great surprise as a guest. It's along the river and is quite the backdrop. The grounds are vast and you can walk around easily or they have golf carts to take you wherever you want to go. I was very sad to leave. I highly recommend this resort and will come back again!

Tentang The Samaya Ubud

Berlokasi di tengah pulau Bali, The Samaya Ubud menawarkan penginapan vila berbintang lima dengan pemandangan taman tropis yang rimbun. Setiap vila memiliki kolam renang pribadi, pusat kebugaran, spa dan hot tub.  Tersedia pula akses WiFi gratis di setiap unit dan seluruh area vila. 

Setiap vila di The Samaya Ubud bernuansa modern kontemporer dengan nuansa hangat. Setiap vila juga dilengkapi dengan televisi layar datar dengan saluran kabel, kulkas serta fasilitas pembuat kopi dan teh. Sementara itu, kamar mandi dalam dilengkapi dengan shower, bathtub, handuk dan perlengkapan mandi.

Selama menginap di The Samaya Ubud, kamu bisa bersantap di Swept Away Restaurant yang menyajikan berbagai hidangan khas Indonesia dan internasional. Kamu juga bisa bersantap di Scene Restaurant yang menyajikan sarapan berupa hidangan khas Indonesia dan internasional sambil menikmati pemandangan bukit hijau dan bentangan sawah padi yang luas. 

Apabila kamu ingin bersantai, kamu bisa memanjakan diri dengan perawatan pijat atau spa yang tersedia di The Spa at The Samaya. Kamu juga mengikuti kelas yoga yang menenangkan di vila ini. Staff vila juga siap membantumu dengan layanan penyewaan sepeda apabila kamu ingin menjelajahi area sekitar vila yang memukau. 

The Samaya Ubud terletak 9 menit berkendara dari Campuhan Ridge Walk, 28 menit berkendara dari Sungai Ayung River dan 54 menit berkendara dari Bandara Internasional Ngurah Rai.

Pertanyaan yang Sering Diajukan

Jenis kamar apa saja yang tersedia di The Samaya Ubud?

Jenis kamar yang tersedia di hotel ini antara lain adalah:

  • Vila 1 Kamar Tidur
  • Vila 1 Kamar Tidur Dengan Pemandangan Taman
  • Vila 1 Kamar Tidur Dengan Pemandangan Sungai
  • Vila 2 Kamar Tidur Dengan Kolam Renang Pribadi
  • Vila 2 Kamar Tidur Dengan Pemandangan Taman

Berapa kisaran harga kamar untuk menginap di The Samaya Ubud?

Harga termurah di The Samaya Ubud kalau kamu mau menginap hari ini adalah IDR 4.440.150

Di mana alamat The Samaya Ubud?

The Samaya Ubud beralamat di Jl. Baung

Pukul berapa waktu check-in & check-out di The Samaya Ubud?

Waktu untuk check-in di The Samaya Ubud adalah mulai dari pukul 14:00-23:59 dan waktu check-out paling lambat pukul 12:00

Apa saja fasilitas yang tersedia di The Samaya Ubud?

Fasilitas yang tersedia dan bisa kamu gunakan di hotel ini adalah (beberapa fasilitas mungkin perlu biaya tambahan):

  • Kolam Renang
  • WiFi
  • Parkir
  • Kolam Renang Private
  • AC

Apakah di The Samaya Ubud tersedia fasilitas kolam renang?

Ya, di The Samaya Ubud tersedia kolam renang yang bisa kamu gunakan.
